We employed contextual words as well as affixes as features. For some context window size d , the complete list of features is:

1) the current word, as well as d preceding and suc- ceeding words;

2) two and three leading characters of the current word and d preceding and succeeding words;

3) two and three trailing characters of the current word and d preceding and succeeding words.
